## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-103">此类型已弃用，并将在 .NET Framework 的未来版本中删除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-103">This type is deprecated and will be removed in a future version of the .NET Framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-104">有关详细信息，请参阅 [Oracle 和 ADO.NET](/dotnet/framework/data/adonet/oracle-and-adonet)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-104">For more information, see [Oracle and ADO.NET](/dotnet/framework/data/adonet/oracle-and-adonet).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-105">不 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 会自动生成对与数据库关联的更改进行协调所需的 SQL 语句 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-105">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> does not automatically generate the SQL statements required to reconcile changes made to a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> associated with the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-106">但是，您可以通过设置的属性，创建一个 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 为单表更新生成 SQL 语句的对象 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-106">However, you can create an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> object that generates SQL statements for single-table updates by setting the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-107">然后，将 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 生成未设置的任何其他 SQL 语句。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-107">Then, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> generates any additional SQL statements that you do not set.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-108">与其对应的之间的关系 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 始终为一对一关系。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-108">The relationship between an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and its corresponding <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> is always one-to-one.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-109">若要创建此函件，请设置 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 对象的属性 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-109">To create this correspondence, you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-110">这会导致将 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 自身注册为侦听器，这会生成 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.RowUpdating> 影响的事件的输出 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-110">This causes the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> to register itself as a listener, which produces the output of <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.RowUpdating> events that affect the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-111">若要生成 INSERT、UPDATE 或 DELETE 语句，请 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 使用 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 属性来检索所需的一组元数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-111">To generate INSERT, UPDATE, or DELETE statements, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> uses the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property to retrieve a required set of metadata.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-112"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder>还使用引用的 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.Connection%2A> 和 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.Transaction%2A> 属性 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-112">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> also uses the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.Connection%2A>, and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.Transaction%2A> properties referenced by the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-113">如果调用 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Dispose%2A> ，将 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 从解除关联 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> ，并且不再使用生成的命令。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-113">If you call <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Dispose%2A>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> is disassociated from the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>, and the generated commands are no longer used.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="160a9-114">下面的示例使用 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 和和 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> 从数据库中选择行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-114">The following example uses <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, along with <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>, to select rows from a database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-115">该示例传递了一个初始化的 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 、一个连接字符串、一个 SQL SELECT 语句的查询字符串和一个作为数据库表名称的字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-115">The example is passed an initialized <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, a connection string, a query string that is an SQL SELECT statement, and a string that is the name of the database table.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="160a9-116">然后，该示例创建一个 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="160a9-116">The example then creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder>.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Private Function SelectOracleRows(connection As String, queryString As String, tableName As String) As DataSet  
  
   Dim connection As New OracleConnection(connection)  
   Dim dataAdapter As New OracleDataAdapter()  
   Dim dataSet As DataSet = New DataSet  
  
   dataAdapter.SelectCommand = New OracleCommand(queryString, connection)  
  
   Dim cmdBuilder As OracleCommandBuilder = New OracleCommandBuilder(dataAdapter)  
  
   connection.Open()  
   dataAdapter.Fill(dataSet, tableName)  
      ' Code to modify data in DataSet here   
      ' Without the OracleCommandBuilder this line would fail.  
   dataAdapter.Update(dataSet, tableName)  
   connection.Close()  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static DataSet SelectOracleSrvRows(string myConnection, string mySelectQuery, string myTableName)  
{  
   OracleConnection myConn = new OracleConnection(myConnection);  
   OracleDataAdapter myDataAdapter = new OracleDataAdapter();  
   myDataAdapter.SelectCommand = new OracleCommand(mySelectQuery, myConn);  
   OracleCommandBuilder cb = new OracleCommandBuilder(myDataAdapter);  
  
   myConn.Open();  
   DataSet ds = new DataSet();  
   myDataAdapter.Fill(ds, myTableName);  
  
   //Code to modify data in DataSet goes here...  
  
   //Without the OracleCommandBuilder this line would fail.  
   myDataAdapter.Update(ds, myTableName);  
   myConn.Close();  
   return ds;  
}  
```
